            <div class="row">

                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 item" style="height: 362px;">
                    <div class="key_features_text">
                        <h5 class="defined_contribution_services">Defined contribution plan consulting and management services include:</h5>

                        <ol class="rounded-list">
                            <li><a href="#">Fiduciary Governance & Documentation</a></li>
                            <li><a href="#">Plan Design Analysis & Benchmarking </a></li>
                            <li><a href="#">Investment Selection and Monitoring </a></li>
                            <li><a href="#">Investment Policy Development </a></li>
                            <li><a href="#">Vendor Search & Selection Processes </a></li>
